WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.230 --> 00:00:03.410
Biz allaqachon tasvirni to‘g‘ri ko‘rsatmoqdamiz, bu Android party rasmi,

00:00:03.410 --> 00:00:06.790
shuning uchun manba atributini 
o‘zgartirishga hojat yo‘q.

00:00:06.790 --> 00:00:09.790
Xuddi shunday, joylashuv ham
noto‘g‘ri emas.

00:00:09.790 --> 00:00:11.920
Rasm faqat biroz kattaroq bo‘lishi kerak, 

00:00:11.920 --> 00:00:15.710
shuning uchun ushbu otaga mos tartib atributlarining barchasi foydalanmoqchi emasmiz.

00:00:15.710 --> 00:00:17.450
Id atributidan foydalanish ham 

00:00:17.450 --> 00:00:21.000
o‘zi-o‘zidan tartibda 
o‘zgarishlarga olib kelmaydi.

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:23.750
Bu shunchaki ko‘rinishga keyinroq murojaat 
qilishingiz mumkin bo‘lishi uchun nom beradi.

00:00:23.750 --> 00:00:27.250
Endi aslida biz xohlagan effektga erishish 

00:00:27.250 --> 00:00:28.980
uchun bizda fon atributi bor.

00:00:28.980 --> 00:00:31.300
Ammo bu rasm ko‘rinishini o‘z ichiga olmaydi.

00:00:31.300 --> 00:00:34.140
Agar fonni tanlagan bo‘lsangiz,
texnik jihatdan to‘g‘ri, lekin

00:00:34.140 --> 00:00:36.010
biz boshqacha tarzda boramiz.

00:00:36.010 --> 00:00:38.060
Biz darsda o‘rgangan yo‘ldan.

00:00:38.060 --> 00:00:41.400
Bu bizni layout_height, layout_width 
va ScaleType atributlari bilan qoldiradi.

00:00:41.400 --> 00:00:44.340
ScaleType rasmning uni o‘rab olgan ko‘rinishdagi

00:00:44.340 --> 00:00:45.380
hajmini o‘zgartiradi.

00:00:45.380 --> 00:00:46.546
Layout_width va

00:00:46.546 --> 00:00:49.940
layout_height aslida ko‘rinish oynasining 
o‘lchamini o‘zgartiradi.

00:00:49.940 --> 00:00:53.530
Bunday holda, rasm etarlicha katta bo‘lib
ko‘rinish oynasini to‘ldirish uchun kengayadi

00:00:53.530 --> 00:00:57.740
u nima bo‘lishidan qat’iy nazar - butun ekranni
o‘ragan tarkib yoki mos keladigan ota.

00:00:57.740 --> 00:01:00.430
Chunki bu alohida holatda bu muhim emas

00:01:00.430 --> 00:01:01.790
biz mos keladigan otani qo‘yamizmi yoki

00:01:01.790 --> 00:01:06.220
o‘ralgan tarkibni, bundan qat’iy nazar
bu holda ularni o‘zgartirishning keragi yo‘q.

00:01:06.220 --> 00:01:09.530
Aytiladiki, biz tasvirni butun ekranni 
egallab olishiga harakat qilyapmiz,

00:01:09.530 --> 00:01:13.350
shuning uchun match parent 
deb o‘rnatish yaxshi bo‘lsa kerak.

00:01:13.350 --> 00:01:15.820
Keyin, agar kichikroq 
rasm bilan tugatsak ham

00:01:15.820 --> 00:01:18.260
u baribir ham butun ekranni to‘ldirib kengayadi.

00:01:18.260 --> 00:01:21.940
Ammo tartib balandligi va kengligi
bu holatda ixtiyoriy bo‘lgani bilan,

00:01:21.940 --> 00:01:25.660
 scale type bu haqiqiy atribut
siz shartli ravishda

00:01:25.660 --> 00:01:27.330
rasm butun ekranni to‘ldirish 
uchun foydalanishingiz kerak.

00:01:28.480 --> 00:01:30.930
Savol shundaki,
biz atributni tanladik, lekin

00:01:30.930 --> 00:01:32.900
 scale type ga beradigan 
qiymatini bilmaymiz

00:01:32.900 --> 00:01:35.710
Va bu men siz keyingi savolda 
aniqlashingizni xohlagan narsa.

